            <div>
              <span class="inline-block bg-carbon text-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">Step 4 ‚Ä¢ Day 5</span>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Review & Feedback</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                We'll send you a preview link. You review, we refine. One round of revisions included.
              </p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Priority support = faster turnaround on any changes</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 5 -->
          <div class="flex gap-6 md:gap-10 border-l-4 border-carbon pl-8 md:pl-12 relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-[13px] top-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-frangipani border-4 border-white"></div>
            <div>
              <span class="inline-block bg-frangipani text-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold mb-3 uppercase tracking-widest">Step 5 ‚Ä¢ Day 6-7</span>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Launch Day üöÄ</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Your premium site goes live. Domain connected. Booking system integrated. Analytics installed. You're officially a digital owner with growth tools.
